==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sundial
<hw>Sun"di`al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An instrument to
show the time of day by means of the shadow of a gnomon, or style, on a
plate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Sundial shell</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>any shell
of the genus Solarium. See <er>Solarium</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sundog</ent>⟦br⟧
